text: The Perfect Candidate is a 2019 Saudi Arabian German drama movie directed by Haifaa al-Mansour and starring Mila Al Zahrani, Nora Al Awadh, Dae Al Hilali. ==Other websites== * Category:2019 drama movies Category:Saudi Arabian movies Category:German drama movies Category:Movies directed by Haifaa al-Mansour
